{
  "texts": [
    "To further refine our selection, a preliminary screening process was initiated, applying stringent criteria that encompassed factors such as title, keywords, language, and abstract.",
    "This rigorous assessment involved the scrutiny of two researchers to ensure both thoroughness and consistency in the selection process.This initial review identified 42 publications that merited further comprehensive analysis.",
    "Subsequently, we conducted a full-text analysis to determine their eligibility.",
    "Our inclusion criteria stated that the studies must specifically address the utilization of the Metaverse in EFL teaching and be supported by empirical data.",
    "A total of 31 publications were carefully included."
  ]
}